                  Car, bus, bike, or motorcycle rentals to match your adventure style and ecological footprint preferences.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            
            <li>
              <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-icon">
                  <ion-icon name="globe-outline"></ion-icon>
                </div>
                <h3 class="value-title">Cultural Immersion</h3>
